&lt;p>&lt;strong>The Role&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>We are looking for creative engineer who enjoy’s being challenged by problems of scale and complexity. As member of the team, you will be working on the systems architecture, systems software, and will get to design and implement novel operating system techniques and algorithms for On-Device Management of Juniper products. &amp;nbsp;As a member of the team you will participate in all phases of software development, including specification, design, implementation, testing and sustaining.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
