&lt;p>&lt;strong>About Juniper&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>At Juniper, we strive to deliver network experiences that transform how people connect, work and live.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>By challenging the inherent complexity in the Cloud + 5G + AI era, our solutions power the connections that matter most - from education to healthcare to secure banking. Our dedication is to advance real outcomes for network teams and every individual they serve.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>It’s that simple!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Why Juniper?&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Our vision is for Juniper Networks to become a multi-generational community that empowers people to accomplish the impossible. This requires a perspective that is multi-generational itself, thinking beyond the markets and products of today and tomorrow to the values that enable a community to prosper for generations. We value trust, integrity, respect, humility, being bold and delivering excellence. We're looking for people who live the values of our culture and can bring our vision to life.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Juniper is looking for sales professionals to develop and close opportunities across a defined list of customers. The candidate will be specific-account focused, and will excel in this dynamic role, while working closely with a team of partner account managers to support growth of their named accounts. You will be responsible for opportunities which will have been identified either through key partners, been advanced from Inside Sales or part of new customer acquisition activity. You will work with partners to break into these accounts by winning deals. The emphasis will be on expanding Juniper’s footprint within the accounts by leveraging specific sales plays.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Primary Responsibilities:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>The Strategic Account Manager will work well in a matrixed environment, building a “virtual” team to drive success of their named account list&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>The Strategic Account Manager will focus on developing the top accounts across Sweden with a plan to penetrate these accounts with partners&lt;/li>
