      &lt;/div>
      &lt;div style="border-width:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;">
       Good understanding of ETSI NFV MANO framework
      &lt;/div>
      &lt;div style="border-width:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;">
       Sound knowledge of Linux architectures and debugging
      &lt;/div>
      &lt;div style="border-width:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;">
       Knowledge in Container based Microservice architectures
      &lt;/div>
      &lt;div style="border-width:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;">
