      &lt;/div>
      &lt;div style="border-width:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;">
       Experience in Designing Multi-cloud&amp;nbsp;Environments
      &lt;/div>
      &lt;div style="border-width:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;">
