&lt;p>&lt;br/>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p></DESCRLONG></JN_CAREERS_SITE_DETAILS><JN_CAREERS_SITE_DETAILS><HRS_JOB_OPENING_ID>1009648</HRS_JOB_OPENING_ID><POSTING_TITLE>Commercial Account Manager</POSTING_TITLE><CITY>Home Office</CITY><STATE>MA</STATE><COUNTRY>USA</COUNTRY><LOCATION_DESCR>Home Office, MA</LOCATION_DESCR><JOB_POSTING_DT>11/28/2023</JOB_POSTING_DT><URL>https://careers.juniper.net/#/jobdescription?jid=1009648</URL><URL_1>https://ejif.fa.us6.oraclecloud.com:443/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX/job/1009648</URL_1><STATE_DESCR>Massachusetts</STATE_DESCR><COUNTRY_DESCR>United States</COUNTRY_DESCR><JOB_CATEGORY_CODE>AM</JOB_CATEGORY_CODE><JOB_CATEGORY_DESCR>Account Management</JOB_CATEGORY_DESCR><RECRUITING_TYPE_CODE>Experienced</RECRUITING_TYPE_CODE><DESCRLONG>
&lt;p>Juniper is looking for sales professionals to develop and close opportunities across a defined list of customers. The candidate will be specific-account focused, and will excel in this multifaceted role while using a team of partner account managers to support the growth of their named account list. You will be responsible for opportunities that will have been identified either through key partners, raised from Inside Sales or as part of new customer acquisition activity. You will work with partners to break into these accounts by winning deals. The emphasis will be on growing Juniper’s footprint within the accounts by demonstrating specific sales plays.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Primary Responsibilities:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>You will work well in a matrixed environment, building a “virtual” team to drive the success of their named account list&lt;/li>
