&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>Expert communication and interpersonal skills.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Effective consultancy, planning &amp; communication skills, excellent interpersonal skills, ability to work on multiple projects and manage customers appropriately.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>The mature “customer first” focus&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Strong planning and designing experience.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Commitment to delivering a remarkable customer experience.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Excellent and deep hands-on and planning capabilities in advanced Data Center technologies – VxLAN, EVPN, MCLAG, IP Fabric&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Strong knowledge of IP-related protocols, including IS-IS, OSPF, BGP, RSVP, LDP, QOS solutions, and IPv6 standards/protocols&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Familiar with any DC fabric SDN/manager/orchestration tool&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Hands-on experience with Linux servers and network services (DHCP, SNMP, FTP, TFTP, DNS, NTP).&lt;/li>
