&lt;p>- IP routing protocol (BGP, OSPF, RIP),&lt;/p>
&lt;p>- Understanding of Multicast related protocol [IGMP,IGMP-snooping, PIM] would be a plus.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>- Scripting skills like Python, Perl, or Shell (bash, ksh, csh) would be considered as added advantage.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
