&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>- Requires B.E. in Electronics Engineering or Computer Science with&amp;nbsp;1- 3&amp;nbsp;years of experience supporting/Designing/implementing IP networks.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>- Candidates who have extensively worked on Troubleshooting, implementation and support of large IP networks.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>&lt;u>Platform Knowledge:&lt;/u>&lt;/strong>&amp;nbsp;Juniper (routers, switches), Cisco, Nortel, Huawei, traffic generators (Ixia, Agilent)/ traffic simulators, protocol analysers, testers etc (not all are required but some of these are good to have).&lt;/p>
