&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Where you’ll work:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>At Juniper, we strive to deliver network experiences that transform how people connect, work and live. We Power Connections, Empower Change, and we do that trough our core values Being Bold, Building Trust and Delivering Excellence.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The role is part of the global Juniper Technical Assistance Center (JTAC) organization. We are a diverse team of dedicated and highly skilled people who represent many nationalities, working in a dynamic and flexible organization, dedicated to delivering better-than-expected support for our customers.&lt;/p>
