&lt;p>Juniper is looking for an Enterprise sales professional to grow our business and market share across a defined list of named accounts within our focus verticals including Large Enterprise (Fortune 1000, Retail, Manufacturing, Tier 2/3 Service Provider and Utility. You will excel in a dynamic and exciting environment while leading all prospecting and sales opportunities across all Juniper solutions. This position is a “hunter” type role where landing new logo’s is the priority. You will report to the Regional Sales Director! Are you ready to join Juniper? &amp;nbsp;&lt;strong>This territory is Columbus/Dayton, Ohio. Need to reside in either City. &lt;/strong>This is a remote position.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Primary Responsibilities:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>Engage, qualify, and develop both new and existing accounts.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Collaborate with SE, Product Specialists, Field Marketing, SDR’s, Partner Account Managers, etc. as well as Juniper’s channel partners.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Understand named account’s technical/operational use cases while driving how they can achieve better network and business outcomes with Juniper.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Lead customer relationship strategy.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Lead personal and Juniper relationships with C-Level, Management, and Decision-Makers.&lt;/li>
