 &lt;li>Lead prospecting, customer meetings and presentations.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Implement Juniper’s sales playbooks.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Lead and/or help with local and regional events, both in-person and virtual.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Lead proposal and opportunity win strategies.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Grow software sales.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Close sales opportunities.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Exceed both current quarter and annual quota.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Win both new logos and new product introductions.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Build an annuity business of franchise customers.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Manage both current and full year for sales pipeline and forecast.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Provide accurate weekly/quarterly sales forecasts while maintain good Salesforce hygiene.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
