&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>Experience with IT networking, specifically WiFi, Switching, SD-WAN and Artificial Intelligence. Full portfolio also includes Routing, Data Center Switching and Security.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Experience with Salesforce.com.&lt;/li>
