&lt;p>&lt;strong>Americas Area Partner Vice President&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The position will report directly to the Vice President of Partner &amp; Commercial Sales.&amp;nbsp; This position will be responsible for leading strategic growth and market expansion in the Americas, focusing on Juniper Networks’ partner ecosystem.&amp;nbsp; This candidate will drive a high-performance culture, set ambitious goals, and achieve results in alignment with the Juniper Way.&amp;nbsp; This person will be the key leader responsible for creating and delivering a strategy plan to drive sales and revenue growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>Strategy Development: Craft and execute innovative strategies to drive sales and revenue growth through Juniper's Partners in the Americas.&lt;/li>
