 &lt;li>Collaboration: Work closely with cross-functional teams and ecosystem partners to develop and implement comprehensive go-to-market plans, ensuring bookings and pipeline goals are achieved.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Sales Analysis: Analyze sales metrics and forecasts, using insights to enhance execution and sales strategies.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Relationship Building: Strengthen relationships with key stakeholders in various sectors, translating technical benefits into valuable solutions.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Industry Awareness: Keep abreast of industry trends, product developments, and competitive landscapes, adapting sales strategies for sustained growth.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Brand Representation: Act as a thought leader at events and forums, enhancing Juniper Networks' presence and building strategic relationships.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Sales Achievement: Consistently meet sales targets, ensure accurate forecasting, and optimize resource use.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
