&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>Sales Leadership: Develop strong relationships with senior sales leadership for cross-functional strategic execution.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Area Partner Sales: Indirect leadership by guiding strategy, support, and sharing best practices.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Support Functions: Collaborate with Partner Marketing, Operations, Finance, HR, Business Development, and Legal teams.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
