 &lt;li>Experience working with distributed teams.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Highly skilled in Agile frameworks and methods, including Lean, Kanban, Scrum.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Familiar with project management frameworks and methods, PMP certification is an added advantage.&lt;/li>
