     &lt;p>Operational day to day admin and maintenance. Planning and forecasting budget&lt;/p>
     &lt;p>Process, Policy and Procedure creation, administration, management and improvement.&lt;/p>
     &lt;p>Ultimately, we’re looking for very experienced, qualified, enthusiastic and self-motivated people that are long term&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong>IT Support&lt;/strong>&amp;nbsp;career-minded. This role will further support career growth within the IT Support arena.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
     &lt;p>&lt;strong>Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
     &lt;ul>
      &lt;li>Manage and distribute incoming incidents, tasks and service requests via all available communication channels including, but not limited to:
       &lt;ul>
        &lt;li>Service Now (Helpdesk)&lt;/li>
