&lt;p>We are looking for a smokejumper who goes distances to make sure customers are wildly successful. A person who communicates with customers, understands their questions as well as solves complex technical issues. You will become the subject matter expert in Enterprise&amp;nbsp;Wireless&amp;nbsp;and Wired Networks. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
