&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>6 months to 3 years of experience in a technical support role in a wireless networking/wireless security company or equivalent education&lt;br/>Strong knowledge required on wireless access points, good troubleshooting and configuration experience.&lt;br/>Strong understanding of Wi-Fi 802.11 networks,&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Triage and Resolve Customer Support Escalations from multiple inbound channels&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
