 &lt;li>Understand features and reproduce customer issues.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>File tickets on bugs found.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Analyze logs and pinpoint root causes.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Work with developers and drive solutions.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Participate in relevant meetings and discussions and provide status reports.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Ask good questions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br/>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
