&lt;p>&lt;strong>Sr. Manager, Compensation:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Juniper Networks Inc., a global leader in Cloud, Data Center, Enterprise, and Security Networking, is seeking an experienced Senior Manager of Compensation to join our world class Total Rewards team. Reporting to the Sr. Director of Compensation, this leadership role is responsible for the design, delivery, and support of regional compensation programs at Juniper and will provide compensation consulting and support to a global line of business. &amp;nbsp;Partners closely with HR Business Partners, regional leaders, and key business stakeholders to provide compensation consulting and support on day to day needs and strategic compensation initiatives. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>&lt;u>Role Responsibilities&lt;/u>&lt;/strong>&lt;br/>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
