 &lt;li>3 years’ experience working with AWS and/or GCP.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Must have technical experience working with EC2 (GCE), IAM, S3 (GS), Kubernetes pods, Jenkins, Prometheus, CloudWatch (Stack Driver), Linux, and Shell Scripting.&lt;/li>
