&lt;p>The IDEAL candidate for this role will be able to demonstrate the following competencies:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
 &lt;li>Strong Knowledge about Core and edge Networks for Service Providers technologies&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>5+ years experience in managing large technical account activity revolving around network products from multiple vendors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
