&lt;p>&lt;strong>About Juniper&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>At Juniper, we strive to deliver network experiences that transform how people connect, work and live.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Juniper Networks was founded on a simple but exceptionally powerful vision for the future of the network: “Connect everything. Empower everyone.” This ideal is the commitment of the company and the mission that drives every Juniper colleague every day.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Juniper Networks brings simplicity to networking with products, solutions, and services that connect the world! Through engineering innovation, we remove the constraints and complexities of networking in the cloud era to solve the toughest challenges our customers and partners face daily.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>At Juniper Networks we believe that the network is a resource for sharing knowledge and human advancement that changes the world. We are committed to imagining groundbreaking ways to deliver automated, scalable, and secure networks to move at the speed of business!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Our products and technology run the world’s largest and most demanding global networks.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Juniper Networks [NYSE: JNPR] is headquartered in Sunnyvale, California, with nearly 9,000+ dedicated employees and offices in nearly 50 countries. Our customers include the top 100 global service providers, 30,000 enterprises, including 99 of the Global Fortune 100, as well as hundreds of federal, state, and local government agencies and higher education organizations.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Why Juniper?&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Our vision is for Juniper Networks to become a multi-generational community that empowers people to accomplish the impossible. This requires a perspective that is multi-generational itself, thinking beyond the markets and products of today and tomorrow to the values that enable a community to prosper for generations. We value trust, integrity, respect, humility, being bold and delivering excellence. We're looking for people who live the values of our culture and can bring our vision to life.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Juniper is looking for sales professionals to develop and close opportunities across a defined list of customers. The candidate will be specific-account focused, and will excel in this dynamic role, while using a team of partner account managers to support growth of their named account list. They will be responsible for opportunities which will have been identified either through key partners, been advanced from Inside Sales or part of new customer acquisition activity. They will work independent and/or with partners to break into these accounts by winning deals. The emphasis will be on expanding Juniper’s footprint within the accounts by leveraging specific sales plays.&lt;/p>
