&lt;div style="border:1.0pt solid #D9D9E3;mso-border-alt:solid #D9D9E3 .25pt;mso-element:para-border-div;padding:0in;">
 &lt;p>&lt;strong>Job Title:&lt;/strong> Go-To-Market (GTM) Sales Technologies Communications and Enablement Specialist&lt;/p>
 &lt;p>&lt;strong>Location:&lt;/strong> Sunnyvale, CA or Westford, MA;&amp;nbsp; preferred&lt;/p>
 &lt;p>&lt;strong>Position Overview:&lt;/strong> We are looking for a skilled and dynamic individual contributor with 5-10 years of experience in Communications and Enablement for Go-To-Market Sales Technologies. The ideal candidate will be responsible for crafting and executing strategic communications plans and enabling our sales teams with the tools, training, and resources they need to excel in selling our technology solutions. Also responsible for developing Communications for internal Executive meetings and, for critical Stakeholders.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
 &lt;p>&lt;strong>Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div style="border:1.0pt solid #D9D9E3;margin-left:.25in;margin-right:0in;mso-border-alt:solid #D9D9E3 .25pt;mso-element:para-border-div;padding:0in 0in 0in 5.0pt;">
 &lt;ul>
  &lt;li>Develop and execute comprehensive communications strategies for GTM Sales Technologies, including product launches, updates, and key initiatives.&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Develop communication plans for internal Executives and Stakeholders.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Create engaging and informative content, including presentations, sales collateral, email communications, and other materials to support sales efforts.&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including product managers, marketing, and sales, to gather information and insights for effective communication.&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Provide guidance and support in the development of sales training programs, ensuring that sales teams have a deep understanding of our technologies.&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Create and maintain a repository of sales enablement resources, including training materials, playbooks, and product documentation.&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Organize and lead training sessions, webinars, and workshops to educate sales teams on product features and benefits.&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Gather feedback from sales teams to continuously improve enablement materials and programs.&lt;/li>
  &lt;li>Monitor and analyze the effectiveness of communications and enablement initiatives, making data-driven adjustments as needed.&lt;/li>
