&lt;p>· Evaluate the implemented data system for variances, discrepancies and efficiencies.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>· Troubleshoot and optimise the existing data flows, models and processing jobs by modularising.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>· Explore ways to enhance the data quality and reliability.&lt;/p>
