&lt;p>· Strong knowledge of spark framework.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>· Understanding the dynamics of a Hadoop cluster ecosystem, with all included services such as spark jobs etc.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>· Enthusiasm to solve any ongoing issues with operating the cluster&lt;/p>
