 &lt;li>3+ yrs. Semiconductor Commodity Management experience&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Experienced and knowledge in semiconductor industry, SerDes technology, memory, and network systems and solutions, semiconductor manufacturing processes and procedures, and sub-tier supply base&lt;/li>
