&lt;ul>
 &lt;li>Layer 3 - IP and related technologies (ICMP, TCP, GRE, QoS, VRRP) IP routing protocols (BGP, OSPF, ISIS)&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Layer 2 technologies (Ethernet, 802.1q/p VLAN, BFD, STP, RSTP, ARP, LACP)&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Multicast protocols [IGMP, IGMP-snooping, PIM]&lt;/li>
