&lt;p>Juniper is seeking a seasoned, results-oriented and high-energy Territory Account Manager to spearhead new sales engagements in the West India territory. This role requires customer engagements as well as close collaboration with Juniper strategic partners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
