&lt;p>You will take charge of developing and implementing strategic commercial opportunity plans, aiming for widespread deployment of Juniper products and services across enterprises. Building and nurturing executive relationships with key decision-makers and influencers will be instrumental in leveraging these connections during the sales process. This will significantly contribute to securing bids, proposals, RFI/RFPs, and Statements of Work.&lt;/p>
