 &lt;li>Ability to logically troubleshoot complex and high impact problems&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Self-learner with appetite for continuous development.&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>In-depth knowledge of the following:&lt;/li>
 &lt;li>Switching Technology [xSTP, VRRP, LACP, Dot1x, COS, QOS]&lt;/li>
