&lt;p>The ideal candidate will have the ability to recruit, develop, and retain top Sales talent. Must have the ability to deliver business value to the accounts and build on customer relationships. Strong technical and business knowledge with complimentary skills to understand the customers business drivers and align to Juniper solutions is essential. Experience in engaging resources including the BUs to drive sales. Must demonstrate the necessary skills to negotiate issues with peers, partners and customers using a Win/Win philosophy.&lt;/p>
