&lt;p>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;strong>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Title: Focal Technical Support Engineer&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p> 
&lt;p>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;strong>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Business Unit: Juniper TAC - Customer Focused Technical Support&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p> 
&lt;p>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;strong>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Job Location: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>USA (&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>TX/MA/VA)&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p> 
&lt;p>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Have you ever used your smartphone, Netflix, cable TV, or WiFi, and wondered how the giants in the cloud and content industry like Amazon, Google, Facebook, and more – sustain the high-speed networks that power our daily lives. Think you’ve got what it takes to support these networks and keep up with their demands or – even better – get ahead of their next challenge? Be a true partner. If so – we might be looking for you for an exciting role in our Customer Focused Technical Support ( CFTS ) team! &lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p> 
&lt;p>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;strong>&lt;span>&lt;span>Summary:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p> 
&lt;ul> 
 &lt;li>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>This position is for the Juniper CFTS (Customer Focused Technical Support) to up-skill on JUNOS based platforms and understands the support process when solving customer issues on JUNOS based products&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>This is an Individual Contributor Role&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Troubleshoot issues related to configuration, hardware, and software, replicate customer environments and network problems in the lab.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Be a customer advocate for timely resolution of the problems reported, understand the environment/network and influence business.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Take ownership for problem resolution, problem reproduction.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/li> 
 &lt;li>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>&lt;span>Be a fast learner and keep pace with newer technologies&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/li> 
